@node "AmyBW" "AmyBW"

 AmyBW is a freeware BlueWave and QWK mailreader created by Leon
 Makkink. Recently we took over the source from Leon as we did before
 with XenoBlue. We hope to release version 2.15 soon.


@endnode

@node "QBlue" "QBlue"

 QBlue is a shareware BlueWave and QWK mailreader created by Paul
 Kienitz. Q-Blue supports all the Blue Wave level 3 packet features.
 The latest and last version is 2.3.

@endnode

@node "Thor" "Thor"

 Thor is a shareware offline mailreader with a messagebase. Copyright
 Ultima Thule Software. It can read many different formats including
 BlueWave. Version 2.4 has many new features in the BlueWave module.


@endnode

